## Remarks  
 This method can be used with the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> class in the following manner.  

```csharp  
try{  
  writer.WriteStartElement(XmlConvert.VerifyName("item"),"bar");  
}  
catch(Exception e)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("error");  
}  
```  



